short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: fortune(6) on your new tab page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Fortune replaces your new tab page with a minimalist page with a random Unix fortune(6) adage each time. The page is entirely local, no remote resource is fetched.
